comment: Amber Heard is abusive.  Johnny Depp is a great actor.
commentable_entity.title: Everyone : Save Grindelwald
commentable_entity.description:
Johnny Depp has been asked to resign from his role as Grindelwald from the Fantastic Beast franchise. Depp as the gentleman he is didn't put up a fight. We as people must support him through this phase. He has been dealing with his toxic ex-wife 'Amber Heard' since their imminent divorce. 

This petition has been put in place to reinstate him effective immediately.
